verbose_text: Whilst IGF1 might synergies with oestrogen in a mitogenic effect on mammary epithelium and at the same time prevent apoptosis, IGFBP3 might limit the bioavailability of IGF1 and at the same time increase apoptosis independently of IGF1.
evidence: prevent apoptosis, IGFBP3 might limit the bioavailability of IGF1
